Install the Mighty core library from Here:  [Mighty Core](https://github.com/MCUdude/MightyCore/)
Add library to Arduino Libraries
Connect Arduino UNO To computer
Ensure proper connections between Arduino and IC as per circuit diagram provided
Open Simple Blink example sketch
Now go to to: Tools > Mighty Core > Atmega 16
Select Programmer as : Arduino as ISP
Go to Sketch > Upload using Programmer

